                <note rend="inline" type="source">890.00/7–2349: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Douglas</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-07-25T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 25, 1949—8 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2602. Plan indicated your 2910 satisfactory. It establishes idea of continuing
                    consultation and exchange of views which is what we desire.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
